Phase 5: Signature Engine v2 & False-Positive Reduction
Overview
This phase implements two major enhancements to SafeImg v2.0:

SignatureEngineV2: Advanced signature matching with wildcards, priority levels, and context awareness
False-Positive Reduction System: Intelligent metadata analysis with confidence scoring and whitelisting
Part 1: SignatureEngineV2
Current Limitations (v1.5)
The existing signature system has several limitations:

Simple string matching only (no wildcards)
No priority or severity levels
No context awareness (same detection everywhere)
Basic JSON schema
Hard-coded signatures mixed with custom loading
Proposed Enhancements
1. Wildcard Support
Allow flexible pattern matching:

{
  "name": "executable_any",
  "pattern": "MZ????", 
  "type": "wildcard",
  "description": "PE executable header with any DOS stub"
}
Wildcard Syntax:

? = any single byte
* = any sequence of bytes (0 or more)
[xx-xx] = byte range (e.g., [00-FF])
{xx,yy,zz} = one of specified bytes
2. Enhanced JSON Schema v2
{
  "version": "2.0",
  "signatures": [
    {
      "name": "php_code",
      "pattern": "<?php",
      "type": "exact",
      "severity": "critical",
      "category": "script",
      "description": "PHP code detected",
      "contexts": ["metadata", "comment", "exif", "xmp"],
      "enabled": true,
      "false_positive_prone": false
    },
    {
      "name": "zip_header_with_method",
      "pattern": "PK\\x03\\x04????{00,08}",
      "type": "wildcard",
      "severity": "high",
      "category": "polyglot",
      "description": "ZIP archive with common compression",
      "contexts": ["embedded", "appended"],
      "enabled": true
    }
  ],
  "whitelist": [
    "benign_base64_thumbnail",
    "adobe_xmp_namespace"
  ]
}
Schema Fields:

name: Unique identifier
pattern: Signature pattern (supports escapes and wildcards)
type
: exact | wildcard | regex
severity
: info | warning | high | critical
category
: script | polyglot | metadata | executable | structure
description: Human-readable description
contexts: Where to search (limits false positives)
enabled: Toggle signature on/off
false_positive_prone: Mark signatures that need confidence scoring
